'''Ian Roberts''' (born [[July 31]], [[1960s#1965|1965]]) portrayed [[Ganwick Trag]] in [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Attack of the Clones'']] (uncredited).

He is an [[Wikipedia:Australian|Australian]] who was formerly a [[Wikipedia:Rugby league|Rugby League]] player, regarded as the first player to be openly gay. He recently made an appearance in [[Wikipedia:Superman Returns|''Superman Returns'']].

